{"tid":868803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【倫常命案】弒母剁頭「12樓丟下」　逆子寫下「人生短短幾十載」字條","createTime":"2018-10-19T19:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T18:54:10.000Z","uid":160807,"like":17,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"85133d9408f40a8ea670759dce9b7ad3e57dbee6","tid":868803,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"狠心弒母的逆子「阿梁」18日晚間因與母親爭吵，竟持菜刀砍下母親頭顱，還將她的頭顱從12樓高處的陽台丟下，導致生母不但身首異處，還頭顱破裂變形無法辨認容貌。另外，阿梁見到警消到場待命後，竟又情緒不穩往樓下狂扔傢俱、拖把等物品，其中還包含兩張疑似和母親相關的字條「人生短短幾十載...話出口多思考」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3632/d3632027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3632%2Fd3632027.jpg&h=83ca31c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲逆子阿梁狠心弒母，現場留有疑似他曾寫下對母親不滿的字條。（圖／記者陳雕文攝，下同）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3632/d3632009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3632%2Fd3632009.jpg&h=b8b60b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在阿梁扔下的物品當中，包含了傢俱、衣褲、球鞋、拖把、光碟片、除濕機等等物品，其中還有兩張疑似寫有對母親不滿的字條「人生短短幾十載，凡事不必太計較，話出口多思考」、「慈悲如母，體恤眾生之苦」，但詳細案情和字條是否確實是逆子阿梁所寫，仍有待警方釐清。<br />\n<br />\n警方查出，逆子的手段相當兇殘、跟據屋內打鬥毀損狀況，顯示死者不斷逃竄躲避，從客廳躲到房間仍難逃逆子持菜刀斬首。梁嫌先拿一把菜刀，在臥室持刀砍斷母親頸動脈後，趁被害人不支倒地，接連用菜刀連砍母親脖子10多刀把生母頭部墮下。警方勘驗現場發現有兩把菜刀沾染血跡，其中一把刀刃嚴重倒捲出現多處缺口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3632/d3632008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3632%2Fd3632008.jpg&h=741c0bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逆子阿梁在狠心弒母後，先是把母親的頭顱從12樓高的陽台丟下，接著又疑似毒癮發作，又拿刀在家裡繼續胡亂揮砍，還將家裡的傢俱胡亂丟下中庭，而落網後又不斷喃喃自語或偶爾咒罵，無法清楚表達情緒。檢警19日早上將偵訊梁姓兇嫌並在中壢殯儀館解剖室勘驗被害人遺體，以釐清死因和逆子行兇動機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3631/d3631655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3631%2Fd3631655.jpg&h=62e816b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181019/1284995.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181019%2F1284995.htm&d=6hvPEzbuRpBcLeQt%2Bf4EHTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6685146b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181019/1284995.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ffe348535a30e5cb6ff3b3cf71c31bbcd9423406","tid":868803,"uid":87582,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:17:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa439e45f59ed4826932e444c92ff662a0fd524","tid":868803,"uid":137504,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:18:55.000Z","msg":"又係道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94709022dcfc309555b840605fa8ab3d1cfde1a2","tid":868803,"uid":11598,"like":185,"dislike":2,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p16.jpg&h=a6eed06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p11.jpg&h=ac2bd972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港代表"},{"pid":"b6fcad276e198c33e48826ce23cef93874b99a00","tid":868803,"uid":43751,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"94709022dcfc309555b840605fa8ab3d1cfde1a2","tid":868803,"uid":11598,"like":185,"dislike":2,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u